  "remarks": "Albert Avdolyan is a Russian businessperson with business interests in the energy sector, especially coal and LNG. Through various companies, notably A-Property-Holdings and Elgaugol, Albert Avodlyan holds significant interests in the Russian energy infrastructure sector, especially coal and LNG. Those economic sectors provide a substantial source of revenue to the Government of the Russian Federation.",
